pan style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">7.操作</span><span style="word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #ff0000; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 14px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444" class="t_tag">系统</span><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">占有率：windows：92%，其中vista 11%，XP 76%。MAC在学校很受欢迎，可以预见以后占有量会增加</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">8.79%</span><span style="word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #ff0000; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 14px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444" class="t_tag">用户</span><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">用MS IE&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">9．比起书本歌曲电影，线上买软件的人只有三分之一</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">10.老美价格敏感，打折、降价对</span><span style="word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #ff0000; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 14px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444" class="t_tag">销售</span><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">影响很大</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">11.系统</span><span style="word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #ff0000; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 14px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444" class="t_tag">工具</span><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">是大头，但是大部分都被反毒反木马和安全软件占据了</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">12.音</span><span style="word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #ff0000; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 14px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444" class="t_tag">视频</span><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">、数码图像处理增长很快</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">13.绝大部分购买途径都是</span><span style="word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #ff0000; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 14px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444" class="t_tag">信用卡</span><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">、借记卡</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">14.老美现在很喜欢计算税费的财务软件和画家族树的软件</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">15.个人增强工具中地图／旅游很受欢迎。除了DVD、CD工具仍很热门以外，我很奇怪screen saver也占大头，不过我确实见</span><span style="word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #ff0000; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 14px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444" class="t_tag">download</span><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">.com里</span><span style="word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #ff0000; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 14px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444" class="t_tag">下载</span><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">量很大</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">16.家庭数码图片&#92;照片处理被ＤＲ强调了几次</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">17.美国人很相信品牌，比较认同更新付费，续费转化率高(说明不用对老美终生免费)&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">18.70%用户在２４小时内下单，５０％在第一个小时，不要指望试用期结束时能有所增加。</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">19.所以好的质量和</span><span style="word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #ff0000; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 14px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444" class="t_tag">界面</span><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">让用户在６０秒内了解并喜欢你的软件是关键</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">20.试用期内大多数用户不会看帮助</span><span style="word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #ff0000; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 14px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444" class="t_tag">文件</span><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">而是转向别的软件</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">21.2%的转化率是非常非常好的转化率(0.5%也大有可为)</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">22.试用期转化率是关键，否则无法做</span><span style="word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #ff0000; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 14px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444" class="t_tag">广告</span><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">、adword、付费search</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">23.本地化</span><span style="word-wrap: break-word; cursor: pointer; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: #ff0000; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 14px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444" class="t_tag">网站</span><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">和软件很重要。20%的用户不下载便购买，值得注意</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">24.网站增加更多地方以及形式的buynow</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">25.网站退出时增加一个购买信息提示</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">26.根据浏览、购买等不同需求设计主页的主入口</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">27.简化页面，重要信息要BOLD，不要scoll</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">28.页面要短句子(标题更短)，每块文字要易复制，排版需要保证打印美观</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">29.软件盒图标能增加1%转化率？销量？</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">30.让用户来帮助本地化是个好主意(当然得有奖励)</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 22.390625px; font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #444444">31.仍有很多美国人对信用卡不放心，网站上有必要证明自己的安全性</span>
